             </font> 
            <p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="1">Hey everyone,<br />
I propose we create an Alliance/Guild/Realm in World of Warcraft when it comes out. Though it has not come out yet it looks VERY promising in that I've not heard anything negative about it from the board whereas SB and DAoC seems to have their fair share of haters and fans.<br />
<br />
Out of all the peeps on the Bert server it seems only 50-75 or so come here on a regular basis and even though we sometimes argue and name call, we do seem to enjoy our time here...<br />
<br />
So, why not move that in-game?<br />
<br />
Sure, you all currently have guildees and buds in-game in 1 or more of the previously named games...but that is probably due to having a common frame of reference. WoW will be unexplored territory with everyone level 1, broke and on unfamiliar ground (except for the storyline)...<br />
<br />
So why not explore it with peeps from here who we already get a kick (good or bad) out of? <br />
<br />
The knowledge and expertise you all have displayed here from in-game tactics and strategy to your RL expertise in computers would make any such Alliance/Guild/Realm a force to be reckoned with...<br />
<br />
Any thoughts?</font></p>
             
            <p></p>
